### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Ping
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ping

###
# BUILD RECOMMENDATIONS
###

### Submit a build request
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/build
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "mid_range_gaming",
  "budget_range": "1000_1500",
  "form_factor": "atx",
  "cpu_brand": "amd",
  "gpu_brand": "nvidia",
  "include_peripherals": false,
  "existing_parts": [],
  "notes": "Prefer quiet components"
}

### List all builds
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/build

### Get a build by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/build/1
